headline.print_headline: Patriots Announce Signing of CB Brandon Browner
headline.main: Patriots Announce Signing of CB Brandon Browner

lead_paragraph: The addition of cornerbacks Darrelle Revis and Brandon Browner gives the New England Patriots' mediocre secondary an improved look.
